      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "An entire year of this kept on\nNow relatively more experienced\nSeeing constant fighting in every corner\nHumans being thrown out in bulk\nBecoming a daily occurrance\n\nThe place had become a battle arena\nThe only way to get through at all\nWas carefully, without incident\n\nNew rules being written every day\nOnly to compensate for other rules\nWritten on other days"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Irresistible",
      "uuid": "f7590475ce7c470a8f69f7ee07438ab4",
      "x": 8304.485639570625,
      "y": 8582.128600318854,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 216.0,
      "z_value": 10.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "An entire year of this!!!!!!!\nyou will pay for what you have done\nand suffer the consequences and accountability\nof the time you have stolen\naway from growth\nas we bury you in a grave\nwhile making you accountable for your actions\nyou monstreous attempt at a human being"
    },
