      "z_value": -9.709000000000161,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "Now wire it into ClaudeResponseNode (which had its own inline pool) and WarmNodeData (default emoji), and NoteEditor (emoji button):",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#5a6a5a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Becoming Yours",
      "uuid": "0f92effd9c944431b575be2d290e11df",
      "x": 19185.643028056922,
      "y": 6586.51877138647,
      "width": 251.1428257563539,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.757000000000135,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "A breath of air\nA second of time\nIt's a visual poem\nA poem about becoming\nAbout growth\nAbout becoming all that you can be\nBecoming Yours, Truly"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "8669e748f77645819c3cff15a674abed",
      "x": 20916.600113720975,
      "y": -751.589656321853,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 204.0,
      "z_value": -9.706000000000163,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "Beautiful reasoning \u2014 the emojis are the one living element that keeps the graph from feeling like a photograph of itself.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#5a6a5a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "8c9467dad77845669d3a21e58f6d3827",
      "x": 21726.839232145234,
      "y": -801.6410220556472,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 176.0,
      "z_value": -9.705000000000163,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "Strip the emoji from serialization \u2014 it never touches the session file, always fresh on load:",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#5a6a5a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "0bfa761e87fa41069b2ac39fc20a848e",
      "x": 19981.971269822825,
      "y": -790.276244004127,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 204.0,
      "z_value": -9.707000000000162,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "Done. One list, one source of truth \u2014 `utils/IconPicker.py` \u2192 `emojiIcons`. ClaudeResponseNode and NoteEditor both draw from it now.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#5a6a5a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "105ddff2eb5141c0b51064c5819a2031",
      "x": 18797.33039916215,
      "y": 2429.243886279496,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 232.0,
      "z_value": -9.703000000000165,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "The emoji is at `r.top() + _BUTTON_ZONE_H + 2` \u2014 that puts it below the button row. To align it with the button row, it should sit inside that top zone:",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
