      "label": "The emoji goes top-left above the button zone, and the button zone + label text both need to shift down to make room. Let me check where the button row is positioned in BaseNode:",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "16d5d664eeeb414dada81b4967601b9e",
      "x": 20421.624189943508,
