      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 316.0,
      "z_value": -9.78200000000012,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "`#6f7f6f` at full opacity. `aboutBgColorFront` (the depth-raised variant) nudged slightly lighter/greener to stay in the same family. The color toggle still works exactly as before \u2014 `node_tint` on the data overrides the default the moment you hit the button.",
